        <div class="footer_section" style="padding:7px 0;"><img width="22" height="22" alt="" src="https://remedicohealth.com/images/fa_feather_globe.png" /> <a href="https://remedicohealth.com/" style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;vertical-align: top;margin-left: 10px;text-decoration: none; color: black; line-height: 24px;color:#515151;">remedicohealth.com</a> </div>

